  "description": "<i>The Takky?</i> (The Table Tennis) is part of the Simple 1500 Series and, naturally, allows you to play a friendly match of ping-pong. The game features three modes: Story mode, where opponents are fought in order; Free mode, where any opponent defeated in Story mode can be played against; and VS mode, where two players choose a character and a stage and go one-on-one. There are ten characters to choose from, and a variety of stage backgrounds.",
